OL,6,FAlthough the repair on the pipe is now
OL,7,Fcomplete, restoring supplies will take
OL,8,Ftime as Southern Water has to recharge
OL,9,Four network and restart our supply
OL,10,Fworks.
OL,12,FThis means disruption is likely to
OL,13,Fcontinue throughout the weekend.
OL,15,FSouthern Water said: " We are working
OL,16,Fhard to deliver to more than 6,000
OL,17,Fcustomers on our Priority Services
OL,18,FRegister, but we know that some
OL,19,Fcustomers are still waiting on
OL,20,Fdeliveries.
